HEADWORD: Colluctancy
<hw>Col*luc"tan*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>colluctari</ets> to struggle with.]</ety> <def>A struggling to
resist; a striving against; resistance; opposition of nature.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

